        public void registerAdditionDataProvider(java.lang.String xpath,
                                         ISCUIAdditionalDataProvider dataProvider,
                                         int priority,
                                         javax.servlet.ServletContext context)
        Utility method to register a data provider for a xpath. xpath XPath of the element/attribute for which data will be provided by the implementation being registered data provider The actual data provider implementation priority The priority with which the data provider needs to be registered. Priority value should be one of the following:
        • FIRST
        • INTERMEDIATE
        • LAST
        context The servlet context

      • hasDataProviderRegistered

        public boolean hasDataProviderRegistered(java.lang.String xpath)
        This method checks if a data provider is registered for the xpath passed as argument. xpath for which data provider has to be checked true if a data provider is registered for the xpath, false otherwise.
